#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &appname;"
msgstr "Uporaba &appname;"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Hiter začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &appname; starts with an empty book collection. To work with "
"some other type of collection, create it using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item, or the button on the toolbar. Collections are "
"populated with some of the more common fields, but you can add, modify, or "
"delete them to suit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je &appname; začne s prazno knjižno zbirko. Če želite delati z "
"drugo vrsto zbirke, jo ustvarite z menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali gumbom v orodni vrstici. Zbirke so poseljene z nekaterimi "
"pogostejšimi polji, vendar jih lahko dodate, spremenite ali izbrišete, da "
"ustrezajo vašim potrebam."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New entries can be added by using the <link linkend=\"entry-editor"
"\"><interface>Entry Editor</interface></link>. The "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Collection</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Entry</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item will open the <interface>Entry Editor</"
"interface> with an empty entry ready for editing. The <interface>Entry "
"Editor</interface> can also be opened by using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Entry Editor</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Once you've entered the values for the "
"entry, you can save it to the collection by using the <guibutton>Save Entry</"
"guibutton> button in the <interface>Entry Editor</interface> dialog, which "
"remains open in case you want to continue adding new entries. Once you've "
"saved an entry in the collection, you can modify it by clicking on it in the "
"main window. If the <interface>Entry Editor</interface> is not already open, "
"you can double click an entry to open the editor and start editing."
msgstr ""
"Nove vnose je mogoče dodati z <link linkend=\"entry-editor"
"\"><interface>urejevalnikom vnosov</interface></link>. Element menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Zbirka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nov vnos</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> odpre <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> s praznim "
"vnosom, pripravljenim za urejanje. <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> "
"lahko odprete tudi z uporabo menijske postavke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži urejevalnik "
"vnosov</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ko vnesete vrednosti za vnos, ga lahko "
"shranite v zbirko z uporabo gumba <guibutton>Shrani vnos</guibutton> v "
"pogovornem oknu <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface>, ki ostane odprt, "
"če želite nadaljevati z dodajanjem novih vnosov. Ko shranite vnos v zbirko, "
"ga lahko spremenite s klikom nanj v glavnem oknu. Če <interface>Urejevalnik "
"vnosov</interface> še ni odprt, lahko dvokliknete vnos, da odprete "
"urejevalnik in začnete urejati."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to include an image in the entry, you can use the standard &kde; "
"File Selector by clicking the <guibutton>Select Image...</guibutton> button "
"in the <link linkend=\"entry-editor\"><interface>Entry Editor</interface></"
"link>, or you can drag an image from the file manager or web browser into "
"the <interface>Entry Editor</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v vnos vključiti sliko, lahko uporabite standardni &kde; izbirnik "
"datotek tako, da kliknete gumb <guibutton>Izberi sliko...</guibutton> v "
"<link linkend=\"entry-editor\"><interface>Urejevalniku vnosov</interface></"
"link> ali pa povlečete sliko iz upravljalnika datotek ali spletnega "
"brskalnika v <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select an entry, the <link linkend=\"entry-view\"><interface>Entry "
"View</interface></link> shows a formatted view of the entry's contents. You "
"can change the template used for showing the entry in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration\"><interface>Configuration Dialog</interface></link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete vnos, <link linkend=\"entry-view\"><interface>Pogled vnosa</"
"interface></link> prikaže oblikovan pogled vsebine vnosa. Predlogo, "
"uporabljeno za prikaz vnosa, lahko spremenite v <link linkend=\"configuration"
"\"><interface>konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</interface></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The entries in the collection are grouped together when they share the same "
"values for certain fields, such as the author or director. You can change "
"the field used for grouping by using the combo box in the toolbar or the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Group Selection</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Vnosi v zbirki so združeni, če imajo enake vrednosti za določena polja, kot "
"je avtor ali režiser. Polje, uporabljeno za združevanje, lahko spremenite z "
"uporabo kombiniranega polja v orodni vrstici ali menijske postavke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbira skupine</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <interface>Quick Filter</interface> in the toolbar to limit "
"the visible entries. The filter is also useful when you want to quickly find "
"an entry. You can type in the title or some other unique word that "
"identifies the entry and the <link linkend=\"detailed-view"
"\"><interface>Column View</interface></link> will only show the entries that "
"match the filter. More complex filtering can use field names directly, such "
"as <emphasis>author=stephenson</emphasis>. The status bar shows you how many "
"entries are in the collection, and how many are currently being filtered."
msgstr ""
"Za omejitev vidnih vnosov lahko uporabite <interface>Hitri filter</"
"interface> v orodni vrstici. Filter je uporaben tudi, ko želite hitro najti "
"vnos. Vnesete lahko naslov ali drugo edinstveno besedo, ki identificira "
"vnos, in <link linkend=\"detailed-view\"><interface>Pogled stolpcev</"
"interface></link> bo prikazal samo vnose, ki ustrezajo filtru. Bolj "
"zapleteno filtriranje lahko neposredno uporablja imena polj, na primer "
"<emphasis>author=stephenson</emphasis>. Vrstica stanja vam pokaže, koliko "
"vnosov je v zbirki in koliko jih je trenutno filtriranih."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Usage"
msgstr "Splošna uporaba"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window has three distinct areas, all of which show information "
"about the collection in a different manner. The primary view is the <link "
"linkend=\"detailed-view\"><interface>Column View</interface></link> in the "
"upper right area, where the value of every field for each entry may be "
"shown. On the left side, tabs hold the <link linkend=\"group-view"
"\"><interface>Group View</interface></link>, which can be used to sort the "
"entries into groups in a tree-structure, the <link linkend=\"filter-view"
"\"><interface>Filter View</interface></link>, which is used to track which "
"entries meet certain criteria, and the <link linkend=\"loan-view"
"\"><interface>Loan View</interface></link>, where any loans are listed. "
"Finally, the <link linkend=\"entry-view\"><interface>Entry View</interface></"
"link> shows a formatted view of the data for a single entry, or an icon view "
"of a group of entries, in the lower right."
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno ima tri različna področja, ki prikazujejo informacije o zbirki "
"na drugačen način. Primarni pogled je <link linkend=\"detailed-view"
"\"><interface>Pogled stolpcev</interface></link> v zgornjem desnem območju, "
"kjer je lahko prikazana vrednost vsakega polja za vsak vnos. Na levi strani "
"zavihki vsebujejo <link linkend=\"group-view\"><interface>Pogled skupine</"
"interface></link>, ki ga lahko uporabite za razvrščanje vnosov v skupine v "
"drevesni strukturi, <link linkend=\"filter-view\"><interface>Pogled filtra</"
"interface></link>, ki se uporablja za sledenje, kateri vnosi izpolnjujejo "
"določena merila, in <link linkend=\"loan-view\"><interface>Loan Pogled</"
"interface></link>, kjer so navedena morebitna posojila. Končno <link linkend="
"\"entry-view\"><interface>Pogled vnosa</interface></link> prikazuje "
"oblikovan pogled podatkov za posamezen vnos ali pogled ikon skupine vnosov v "
"spodaj desno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &appname; Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavno okno &appname;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &appname; Main Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavno okno &appname;</phrase>"

#. Tag: interface
#: fundamentals.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column View"
msgstr "Pogled stolpca"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any of the fields in the collections may be shown in the <interface>Column "
"View</interface>, although <emphasis><link linkend=\"para\">Paragraph</"
"link></emphasis>, <emphasis><link linkend=\"image\">Image</link></emphasis>, "
"and <emphasis><link linkend=\"table\">Table</link></emphasis> fields will "
"probably not be useful. Right-clicking on the header of the view opens a "
"menu for selecting the visible fields. The columns may be resized and "
"reordered in any way, and the settings will be saved between sessions."
msgstr ""
"Katera koli polja v zbirkah so lahko prikazana v <interface>Pogledu "
"stolpcev</interface>, čeprav <emphasis><link linkend=\"para\">Odstavek</"
"link></emphasis>, <emphasis><link linkend=\"image\">Slika</link></emphasis> "
"in <emphasis><link linkend=\"table\">Tabela</link></emphasis> verjetno ne "
"bodo uporabni. Z desnim klikom na glavo pogleda se odpre meni za izbiro "
"vidnih polj. Stolpcem je mogoče spreminjati velikost in vrstni red na "
"kakršenkoli način, nastavitve pa bodo shranjene med sejami."

#. Tag: interface
#: fundamentals.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Group View"
msgstr "Skupinski pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Group View</interface> groups the entries in a tree-view by "
"any field which <link linkend=\"field-options\">allows grouping</link>. The "
"number of entries in each group is shown next to the group name. Groups may "
"be expanded or collapsed by clicking the arrow sign, or by double-clicking "
"the item. Expanding and contracting all the groups are options in the right-"
"click context menu. The tree may be sorted either by the group name, or by "
"the count, by clicking on the header. A group may also be used as a filter "
"for the <link linkend=\"detailed-view\"><interface>Column View</interface></"
"link>, by right-clicking on the group item."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Pogled skupine</interface> združuje vnose v drevesnem pogledu "
"glede na katero koli polje, ki <link linkend=\"field-options\">omogoča "
"združevanje</link>. Število vnosov v posamezni skupini je prikazano poleg "
"imena skupine. Skupine lahko razširite ali strnete s klikom na znak puščice "
"ali z dvojnim klikom na predmet. Razširitev in krčenje vseh skupin sta "
"možnosti na desni -kliknite kontekstni meni. Drevo je lahko razvrščeno po "
"imenu skupine ali na njihovo število, s klikom na glavo. Skupino lahko "
"uporabite tudi kot filter za <link linkend=\"detailed-view"
"\"><interface>Pogled stolpcev</interface></link>, z desnim klikom na element "
"skupine."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When more than one field in the collection has the <emphasis><link linkend="
"\"fields-dialog\"><guilabel>Format as a name</guilabel></link></emphasis> "
"option turned on, an additional group is added to combine all those fields "
"into one single <emphasis>People</emphasis> pseudo-group."
msgstr ""
"Kadar ima več kot eno polje v zbirki povezavo vklopljeno možnost "
"<emphasis><link linkend=\"fields-dialog\"><guilabel>Oblikuj kot ime</"
"guilabel></link></emphasis>, je dodana dodatna skupina, ki združuje vsa ta "
"polja v eno samo psevdoskupino <emphasis>Ljudje</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an entry does not contain a value for the field being used to form the "
"groups, it is placed in the <emphasis>(Empty)</emphasis> group, which uses a "
"red folder."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &appname; začne s prazno knjižno zbirko. Če želite delati z drugo "
"vrsto zbirke, jo ustvarite z menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali gumbom v orodni vrstici. Zbirke so poseljene z nekaterimi "
"pogostejšimi polji, vendar jih lahko dodate, spremenite ali izbrišete, da "
"ustrezajo vašim potrebam."

#. Tag: interface
#: fundamentals.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter View"
msgstr "Filtriraj pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If any filters are saved for the collection, the <interface>Filter View</"
"interface> becomes active. As you add or modify entries, they will "
"automatically be checked against the filters and add or removed as "
"appropriate. The filter may be modified by double-clicking on the item to "
"open the <link linkend=\"filter-dialog\"><interface>Advanced Filter Dialog</"
"interface></link>. Right-clicking gives you the option to delete it "
"altogether."
msgstr ""
"Če so za zbirko shranjeni filtri, <interface>Pogled filtra</interface> "
"postane aktiven. Ko dodate ali spremenite vnose, se bodo samodejno preverili "
"glede na filtre in dodali ali odstrani kot je primerno. Filter lahko "
"spremenite z dvojnim klikom na predmet odpri okno <link linkend=\"filter-"
"dialog\"><interface>Napredni filter</interface></link>. Z desnim klikom "
"lahko izbrišete vse skupaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The <interface>Filter View</interface></screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo><interface>Pogled filtra</interface></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The <interface>Filter View</interface></phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><interface>Pogled filtra</interface></phrase>"

#. Tag: interface
#: fundamentals.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan View"
msgstr "Pogled izposoje"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once entries are checked-out on loan, the <interface>Loan View</interface> "
"is added to the window, so those borrowed entries may be tracked. Loans are "
"tracked on a per-entry bases, so right-clicking on an entry item has an "
"option for modifying the loan using the <interface>Loan Dialog</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vnosi za izposojo zabeleženi, se <interface>Pogled izposoje</"
"interface>doda v okno, tako da je tem izposojenim vnosom mogoče slediti. "
"Izposoje se sledijo na osnovi vnosa, tako da ima desni klik na element vnosa "
"možnost za spreminjanje izposoje z uporabo <interface>pogovornega okna za "
"izposojo</interface>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The <interface>Loan View</interface></screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo><interface>Pogled izposoje</interface></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The <interface>Loan View</interface></phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><interface>Pogled izposoje</interface></phrase>"

#. Tag: interface
#: fundamentals.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entry View"
msgstr "Pogled vnosa"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A formatted representation of the entry's values is shown in the "
"<interface>Entry View</interface>. Templates are used for the layout and any "
"additional graphics. Separate templates for each type of collection may be "
"specified in the <link linkend=\"template-options\"><interface>Configuration "
"Dialog</interface></link>, along with custom colors and fonts."
msgstr ""
"Oblikovana predstavitev vrednosti vnosa je prikazana v<interface>Vstopni "
"pogled</interface>. Predloge se uporabljajo za postavitev in poljubnedodatne "
"grafike. Za vsako vrsto zbirke so lahko ločene predlogedoločeno v <link "
"linkend=\"template-options\"><interface>konfiguracijiPogovorno okno</"
"interface></link>, skupaj z barvami in pisavami po meri."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All of the default templates honor the color and font selection, but other "
"custom templates might not. The default templates also make &URL; fields "
"active, which will open up with the default &kde; file association. When "
"exporting to &HTML;, the current template is used for exporting the "
"individual entry files."
msgstr ""
"Vse privzete predloge upoštevajo izbiro barve in pisave, vendar druge "
"predloge po meri morda ne. Privzete predloge tudi &URL; aktivirajo polja, ki "
"se bodo odprla s privzetimi &kde; povezavami datotek. Ko se izvozi v &HTML;, "
"se trenutna predloga uporablja za izvoz posamezne vnosne datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statusbar"
msgstr "Vrstica stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar is used to show you what &appname; is currently doing. It "
"also includes a total count of the entries in the collection, and if a "
"filter is being used, how many are currently visible."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica stanja se uporablja za prikaz, kaj &appname; trenutno počne. "
"Vključuje tudi skupno število vnosov v zbirki in, če je uporabljen filter, "
"koliko jih je trenutno vidnih."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Entries"
msgstr "Urejanje vnosov"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> is used to add and modify entries in "
"the collection. Double-clicking on an entry in either the <interface>Group "
"View</interface> or the <interface>Column View</interface> opens the "
"<interface>Entry Editor</interface> with that entry. New entries may be "
"created using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Collection</guimenu></menuchoice> "
"menu, the toolbar icon, or the button in the <interface>Entry Editor</"
"interface> itself."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> se uporablja za dodajanje in "
"spreminjanje vnosov v zbirki. Dvoklik na vnos v <interface>Pogled skupine</"
"interface> ali <interface>Pogled stolpcev</interface> odpre "
"<interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> s tem vnosom. Nove vnose lahko "
"ustvarite z uporabo menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Zbirka</guimenu></"
"menuchoice>, ikone v orodni vrstici ali gumba v samem "
"<interface>Urejevalniku vnosov</interface>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closing the <interface>Entry Editor</interface> when changes have been made "
"but not saved will cause a warning message to appear. The fields are grouped "
"by category and appear in the order that they appear in the <link linkend="
"\"fields-dialog\"><interface>Collection Fields Dialog</interface></link>. "
"They may also be reordered."
msgstr ""
"Če zaprete <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface>, ko so bile spremembe "
"narejene, vendar niso shranjene, se prikaže opozorilno sporočilo. Polja so "
"razvrščena po kategorijah in prikazana v vrstnem redu, kot so prikazana v "
"<link linkend=\"fields-dialog\"><interface>pogovornem oknu Polja zbirke</"
"interface></link>. Lahko se jih tudi prerazporedi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface></screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface></phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the field title for a <link linkend=\"url\"><emphasis>&URL;</"
"emphasis></link> field will open the link using the default &kde; file "
"association. The <guiicon>&URL; selector</guiicon> button beside the text "
"entry will open the default &kde; File Open Dialog, but the field is not "
"limited to local files."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete naslov polja za polje <link linkend=\"url\"><emphasis>&URL;</"
"emphasis></link>, se odpre povezava s privzetim &kde; povezava datotek. "
"<guiicon>&URL; izbirni gumb</guiicon> poleg vnosa besedila bo odprl privzeti "
"&kde; Pogovorno okno za odpiranje datoteke, vendar polje ni omejeno na "
"lokalne datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For <link linkend=\"image\"><emphasis>Image</emphasis></link> fields, the "
"<guibutton>Select Image...</guibutton> button opens up the &kde; image file "
"selection dialog. The image is saved in the collection in the original "
"format, and a scaled version is shown in the <interface>Entry Editor</"
"interface>. The image may be cleared by using the <guibutton>Clear</"
"guibutton> button. Cleared images are removed from the collection."
msgstr ""
"Za polja <link linkend=\"image\"><emphasis>Slika</emphasis></link> gumb "
"<guibutton>Izberi sliko ...</guibutton> odpre &kde; pogovorno okno za izbiro "
"slikovne datoteke. Slika je shranjena v zbirki v izvirni obliki, pomanjšana "
"različica pa je prikazana v <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface>. Sliko "
"lahko počistite z gumbom <guibutton>Počisti</guibutton>. Počiščene slike so "
"odstranjene iz zbirke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> for <emphasis>Image</"
"emphasis> fields</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> za polja "
"<emphasis>Slika</emphasis></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> for <emphasis>Image</"
"emphasis> fields</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> za polja <emphasis>Slika</"
"emphasis></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The edit widget also supports drag-and-drop. Dragging an image file from a "
"file-manager or browser window does the same thing as selecting the image in "
"the File Selector. Dragging an image from the edit widget into a &konqueror; "
"file manager window will save the image in that folder."
msgstr ""
"Pripomoček za urejanje podpira tudi povleci in spusti. Če povlečete slikovno "
"datoteko iz upravitelja datotek ali okna brskalnika, naredite isto kot če "
"izberete sliko v izbirniku datotek. Vlečenje slike iz gradnika za urejanje v "
"&konqueror; okno upravitelja datotek bo sliko shranilo v to mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the images are stored in the collection data file, keeping "
"everything contained in one location. However, too many images will cause "
"&appname; to slow down significantly as well result in a very large data "
"file. Alternatively, &appname; can save the images separately, either in the "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/tellico/data/</filename> folder "
"or in a folder in the same location as the data file. Loading and saving "
"data files is much faster if images are stored separately, but the data "
"files are no longer portable or archivable. Self-contained data files can "
"always be created by using the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenu>Export</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export to Zip...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Slike so privzeto shranjene v podatkovni datoteki zbirke, tako da je vse na "
"enem mestu. Vendar pa bo zaradi preveč slik &appname; da se znatno upočasni, "
"povzroči tudi zelo veliko podatkovno datoteko. Druga možnost je, da "
"&appname; lahko slike shranite ločeno, bodisi v mapo <filename class="
"\"directory\">~/.local/share/tellico/data/</filename> ali v mapo na istem "
"mestu kot podatkovno datoteko. Nalaganje in shranjevanje podatkovnih datotek "
"je veliko hitrejše, če so slike shranjene ločeno, vendar podatkovne datoteke "
"niso več prenosljive ali arhivirane. Samostojne podatkovne datoteke lahko "
"vedno ustvarite z uporabo menijske postavke <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenu>Izvoz</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvoz v Zip...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"table\"><emphasis>Table</emphasis></link> fields begin with "
"five rows, but moving the cursor to the last row automatically adds another. "
"For multi-column tables, only the first column is used for grouping or "
"formatting."
msgstr ""
"Polja <link linkend=\"table\"><emphasis>Tabela</emphasis></link> se začnejo "
"s petimi vrsticami, vendar se s premikanjem kazalca v zadnjo vrstico "
"samodejno doda še ena. Pri tabelah z več stolpci se za združevanje ali "
"oblikovanje uporablja samo prvi stolpec."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> for <emphasis>Table</"
"emphasis> fields</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> za polja "
"<emphasis>tabele</emphasis></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> for <emphasis>Table</"
"emphasis> fields</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> za polja <emphasis>tabele</"
"emphasis></phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Multiple Entries"
msgstr "Urejanje več vnosov"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Multiple entries may be edited at the same time by selecting more than one "
"in either the <interface>Group View</interface> or the <interface>Column "
"View</interface>. If multiple entries are selected, the fields which contain "
"the same value in every entry are enabled. If entries have different values, "
"then the fields are disabled. Check boxes are added to the extreme right for "
"each field entry which control whether the field is enabled or not, as shown "
"in the screenshot below."
msgstr ""
"Več vnosov je mogoče urejati hkrati, tako da izberete več kot enega v "
"<interface>pogledu skupine</interface> ali <interface>pogledu stolpcev</"
"interface>. Če je izbranih več vnosov, so omogočena polja, ki vsebujejo isto "
"vrednost v vsakem vnosu. Če imajo vnosi različne vrednosti, so polja "
"onemogočena. Potrditvena polja so dodana skrajno desno za vsak vnos v polje, "
"ki nadzorujejo, ali je polje omogočeno ali ne, kot je prikazano na spodnjem "
"posnetku zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only enabled fields will be modified when the entries are saved, which makes "
"large-scale editing much easier. For example, to set the Medium of all the "
"video entries in the collection, make sure the Medium field is enabled. "
"Change it to <acronym>DVD</acronym>, then save the entries. Only the Medium "
"field will be modified, preserving all the other field values for the "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Ko bodo vnosi shranjeni, bodo spremenjena samo omogočena polja, kar "
"poenostavi obsežno urejanje. Če želite na primer nastaviti medij vseh video "
"vnosov v zbirki, se prepričajte, da je omogočeno polje medij. Spremenite ga "
"v <acronym>DVD</acronym>, nato shranite vnose. Spremenjeno bo samo polje "
"Srednje, pri čemer bodo ohranjene vse druge vrednosti polj za vnose."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> for multiple entries</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> za več vnosov</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> for multiple entries</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase><interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> za več vnosov</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updating Entry Data"
msgstr "Posodabljanje vnosnih podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries may be automatically updated by querying the data sources available "
"for the current collection type, which is very useful for combining "
"information from multiple sources. For example, you may add a movie to your "
"collection using the <link linkend=\"amazon-web-services\">Amazon.com Web "
"Services</link>, and then update the entry with additional information from "
"the <link linkend=\"imdb\">Internet Movie Database</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vnose je mogoče samodejno posodobiti s poizvedovanjem podatkovnih virov, ki "
"so na voljo za trenutno vrsto zbirke, kar je zelo uporabno za združevanje "
"informacij iz več virov. Na primer, lahko dodate film v svojo zbirko s "
"pomočjo <link linkend=\"amazon-web-services\">spletnih storitev Amazon.com</"
"link> in nato posodobite vnos z dodatnimi informacijami iz <link linkend="
"\"imdb\">Internet Movie Database</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only empty fields are updated unless the <link linkend=\"data-sources-options"
"\">setting for that source</link> allows results to overwrite existing "
"information. For <link linkend=\"externalexec\">external scripts</link>, an "
"update field must be specified in the source options."
msgstr ""
"Posodobljena so samo prazna polja, razen če <link linkend=\"data-sources-"
"options\">nastavitev za ta vir</link> omogoča, da rezultati prepišejo "
"obstoječe informacije. Za <link linkend=\"externalexec\">zunanje skripte</"
"link> mora biti polje za posodobitev podano v možnostih vira."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The entry updating may be started via the right-click menu for an entry, or "
"by using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Collection</guimenu><guimenuitem>Update "
"Entry</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Posodabljanje vnosa lahko začnete prek menija z desnim klikom za vnos ali z "
"uporabo menijske postavke <menuchoice><guimenu>Zbirka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi vnos</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Fields"
msgstr "Urejanje polj"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Collection Fields Dialog</interface> allows you to add new "
"fields to the collection, to modify the existing ones, or to delete fields "
"altogether."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Pogovorno okno Polja zbirke</interface> vam omogoča dodajanje "
"novih polj v zbirko, spreminjanje obstoječih ali popolno brisanje polj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The &appname; <interface>Collection Fields Dialog</interface></"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno polj zbirke</interface></"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The &appname; <interface>Collection Fields Dialog</interface></"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno polj zbirke</interface></phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Field List"
msgstr "Seznam polj"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side of the dialog is the list of the current fields. Modified "
"fields are shown in bold italics. The buttons below the list will add or "
"delete a field, and the arrows can be used to change their order. The order "
"of the fields in the list is important because the <interface>Entry Editor</"
"interface> uses the order for its layout. For each category, the fields will "
"be laid out from left to right, according to the top-to-bottom order of the "
"fields in the list."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani pogovornega okna je seznam trenutnih polj. Spremenjena polja "
"so prikazana v krepkem poševnem tisku. Gumbi pod seznamom bodo dodali ali "
"izbrisali polje, s puščicami pa lahko spremenite njihov vrstni red. Vrstni "
"red polj na seznamu je pomemben, ker <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</"
"interface> uporablja vrstni red za svojo postavitev. Za vsako kategorijo "
"bodo polja razporejena od leve proti desni, glede na vrstni red polj na "
"seznamu od zgoraj navzdol."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Field Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti polja"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A field is defined by its title, type, category, description, and possibly a "
"default value or some allowed values. The title is used everywhere to refer "
"to the field in the user interface. The <interface>Entry Editor</interface> "
"uses it to prompt for values. The <interface>Column View</interface> uses it "
"as a column header. The different types of fields are <link linkend=\"field-"
"types\">explained in the Field Types section</link>. The description is used "
"as a tooltip in the <interface>Entry Editor</interface>, perhaps to provide "
"an explanation of the field's contents. In addition, for <link linkend="
"\"derived\">fields with <emphasis>derived</emphasis> values</link>, a value "
"template is used to format the field's value. The default value is "
"automatically added when creating a new entry. The list of allowed values "
"for <link linkend=\"choice\"><emphasis>Choice</emphasis></link> fields "
"should be separated by a semi-colon."
msgstr ""
"Polje je definirano z naslovom, tipom, kategorijo, opisom in morebitno "
"privzeto vrednostjo ali nekaterimi dovoljenimi vrednostmi. Naslov se povsod "
"uporablja za sklicevanje na polje v uporabniškem vmesniku. "
"<interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface> ga uporablja za pozive k "
"vrednostim. <interface>Pogled stolpca</interface> ga uporablja kot glavo "
"stolpca. Različne vrste polj so <link linkend=\"field-types\">razložene v "
"razdelku Vrste polj</link>. Opis se uporablja kot namig v "
"<interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface>, morda za razlago vsebine polja. "
"Poleg tega se za <link linkend=\"derived\">polja z <emphasis>izpeljanimi</"
"emphasis> vrednostmi</link> uporabi predloga vrednosti za oblikovanje "
"vrednosti polja. Privzeta vrednost se samodejno doda pri ustvarjanju novega "
"vnosa. Seznam dovoljenih vrednosti za polja <link linkend=\"choice"
"\"><emphasis>Choice</emphasis></link> mora biti ločen s podpičjem."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:266
