#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Field Options"
msgstr "Možnosti polja"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fields also have three general options. If auto-completion is enabled, "
"&appname; caches the values for each field, and the <interface>Entry Editor</"
"interface> offers automatic completion, using the standard &kde; settings. "
"Not all field types allow auto-completion. &appname; also needs to know if a "
"field may have multiple values or may be used to group the entries. A semi-"
"colon is used to separate multiple values when editing an entry."
msgstr ""
"Polja imajo tudi tri splošne možnosti. Če je omogočeno samodejno dokončanje, "
"&appname; predpomni vrednosti za vsako polje, <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</"
"interface> pa ponuja samodejno izpolnjevanje z uporabo standardnega &kde; "
"nastavitve. Vse vrste polj ne omogočajo samodokončanja. &appname; prav tako "
"mora vedeti, ali ima lahko polje več vrednosti ali se lahko uporablja za "
"združevanje vnosov. Podpičje se uporablja za ločevanje več vrednosti pri "
"urejanju vnosa."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For efficiency, do not enable auto-completion unless you need it for the "
"fields. The more fields with auto-completion in the collection, the slower "
"it takes &appname; to load the file."
msgstr ""
"Zaradi učinkovitosti ne omogočite samodokončanja, razen če ga potrebujete za "
"polja. Več kot je polj s samodopolnjevanjem v zbirki, počasneje &appname; da "
"naložite datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering Entries"
msgstr "Filtriranje vnosov"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Advanced Filter Dialog</interface> allows you to limit the "
"entries visible in the <link linkend=\"detailed-view\"><interface>Column "
"View</interface></link> to those that match one or more filter rules. The "
"filter may be used to find the entries that meet all of the rules in the "
"dialog, or just to find those that meet any of them. The <interface>Advanced "
"Filter Dialog</interface> is also useful for advanced searching within a "
"collection."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Pogovorno okno naprednega filtra</interface> vam omogoča, da "
"omejite vnose, vidne v <link linkend=\"detailed-view\"><interface>pogledu "
"stolpcev</interface></link> na tiste, ki se ujemajo z enim ali več pravila "
"filtra. Filter lahko uporabite za iskanje vnosov, ki izpolnjujejo vsa "
"pravila v pogovornem oknu, ali samo za iskanje tistih, ki izpolnjujejo "
"katero koli od njih. <interface>Pogovorno okno naprednega filtra</interface> "
"je prav tako uporabno za napredno iskanje znotraj zbirke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The &appname; <interface>Advanced Filter Dialog</interface></"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno naprednega filtra</"
"interface></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The &appname; <interface>Advanced Filter Dialog</interface></phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno naprednega filtra</interface></"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each row contains a single filter rule. Select the field to match in the "
"first box in the row, then select a matching rule in the center. Rules may "
"match values that contain a certain word, or are exactly equal. A regular "
"expression may also be used to match entries, in which case the "
"<guibutton>Edit...</guibutton> button becomes active for editing the "
"expression, if &kregexpeditor; is installed on your computer. Finally, the "
"word or string to match should be entered in the text box. For image fields, "
"the image size can be used for filtering where the filter value is compared "
"against the larger image dimension, whether width or height."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka vrstica vsebuje eno pravilo filtra. Izberite polje za ujemanje v prvem "
"polju v vrstici, nato izberite pravilo za ujemanje na sredini. Pravila se "
"lahko ujemajo z vrednostmi, ki vsebujejo določeno besedo, ali so popolnoma "
"enake. Za ujemanje vnosov se lahko uporabi tudi regularni izraz, v tem "
"primeru postane gumb <guibutton>Uredi ...</guibutton> aktiven za urejanje "
"izraza, če &kregexpeditor; je nameščen na vašem računalniku. Nazadnje je "
"treba v besedilno polje vnesti besedo ali niz, ki se ujema. Pri slikovnih "
"poljih se lahko velikost slike uporabi za filtriranje, kjer se vrednost "
"filtra primerja z večjo dimenzijo slike, bodisi širino ali višino."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Up to eight (8) rules may be used in the filter. The <guibutton>More</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Fewer</guibutton> buttons may be used to add or "
"remove rules."
msgstr ""
"V filtru lahko uporabite do osem (8) pravil. Gumba <guibutton>Več</"
"guibutton> in <guibutton>Manj</guibutton> lahko uporabite za dodajanje ali "
"odstranjevanje pravil."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Filters may be saved, so that all entries which match are grouped together "
"in the <interface>Filter View</interface>. The view is dynamic, so as "
"entries are added or modified, the group is automatically updated. To save "
"the filter, enter a name in the text box, and click the <guibutton>Save "
"Filter</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Filtre je mogoče shraniti, tako da so vsi vnosi, ki se ujemajo, združeni v "
"<interface>Pogled filtra</interface>. Pogled je dinamičen, tako da se "
"skupina samodejno posodablja, ko so vnosi dodani ali spremenjeni. Če želite "
"shraniti filter, vnesite ime v besedilno polje in kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Shrani filter</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Previously saved filters may be modified by right-clicking on the filter "
"item in the <interface>Filter View</interface> and selecting "
"<guilabel>Modify Filter</guilabel>. The <interface>Advanced Filter Dialog</"
"interface> is opened, and changes may be made to the filter's name or rules."
msgstr ""
"Prej shranjene filtre lahko spremenite tako, da z desnim klikom na element "
"filtra v <interface>Pogled filtra</interface> izberete <guilabel>Spremeni "
"filter</guilabel>. Odpre se <interface>Pogovorno okno naprednega filtra</"
"interface> in lahko spremenite ime ali pravila filtra."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To find the science fiction books you've not read, check the <guilabel>Match "
"all of the following</guilabel> button, set the first rule to "
"<emphasis>Genre contains Science Fiction</emphasis> and the second to "
"<emphasis>Read does not contain true</emphasis>. (For <link linkend=\"bool"
"\">Checkbox</link> fields, the internal value is <emphasis>true</emphasis>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati znanstvenofantastične knjige, ki jih niste prebrali, "
"označite gumb <guilabel>Ujemaj vse naslednje</guilabel>, nastavite prvo "
"pravilo na <emphasis>Žanr vsebuje znanstveno fantastiko</emphasis> in drugo "
"na <emphasis >Prebrano ne vsebuje resnice</emphasis>. (Za polja <link "
"linkend=\"bool\">Potrditveno polje</link> je notranja vrednost "
"<emphasis>true</emphasis>)."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To find the books by Bujold or Weber, check the <guilabel>Match any of the "
"following</guilabel> button, set the first rule to <emphasis>Author contains "
"Bujold</emphasis> and the second to <emphasis>Author contains Weber</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati knjige Bujolda ali Webra, označite gumb <guilabel>Ujemaj "
"se s katerim koli od naslednjih</guilabel>, nastavite prvo pravilo na "
"<emphasis>Avtor vsebuje Bujolda</emphasis> in drugo na <emphasis>Avtor "
"vsebuje Weber </emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generating Reports"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje poročil"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; can generate various reports about your current collection. The "
"<interface>Report Dialog</interface> checks for all &xslt; templates in the "
"installation path and in <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/"
"tellico/report-templates/</filename>. So you can create new ones, and they "
"are automatically found and included as options in the <interface>Report "
"Dialog</interface>. Some complex reports may take a while to generate for "
"large collections."
msgstr ""
"&appname; lahko ustvari različna poročila o vaši trenutni zbirki. "
"<interface>Pogovorno okno za poročilo</interface> preveri vse &xslt; "
"predloge v namestitveni poti in v <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/"
"share/tellico/report-templates/</filename>. Tako lahko ustvarite nove, ki se "
"samodejno najdejo in vključijo kot možnosti v <interface>Pogovorno okno za "
"poročilo</interface>. Ustvarjanje nekaterih kompleksnih poročil za velike "
"zbirke lahko traja nekaj časa."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The templates that are installed with &appname; include a list of titles "
"only, the default column view, a group view, a summary of all of the groups "
"and the most popular values in those groups, a loan report, and a large "
"report with cover images. Select the desired template and click the "
"<guibutton>Generate</guibutton> button. Any report may also be printed or "
"saved to an &HTML; file."
msgstr ""
"Predloge, ki so nameščene z &appname; vključujejo samo seznam naslovov, "
"privzeti pogled stolpcev, pogled skupine, povzetek vseh skupin in najbolj "
"priljubljenih vrednosti v teh skupinah, poročilo o izposoji in veliko "
"poročilo s slikami naslovnice. Izberite želeno predlogo in kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Ustvari</guibutton>. Vsako poročilo je mogoče tudi natisniti ali "
"shraniti v &HTML; mapa."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The &appname; <interface>Report Dialog</interface></screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno poročila</interface></"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &appname; <interface>Report Dialog</interface></phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno poročila</interface></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The entries included in the report will be limited to the ones in the "
"<interface>Column View</interface> so if you've got an active filter, the "
"<interface>Report Dialog</interface> will use it."
msgstr ""
"Vnosi, vključeni v poročilo, bodo omejeni na tiste v <interface>pogledu "
"stolpcev</interface>, tako da če imate aktiven filter, ga bo "
"<interface>pogovorno okno za poročilo</interface> uporabilo."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loan Tracking"
msgstr "Sledenje izposoji"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; supports tracking loans of any entries in the collection. The "
"<interface>Loan Dialog</interface> may be opened by using the "
"<guilabel>Check-out</guilabel> menu item, or right-clicking on an entry. "
"Multiple entries may be checked-out at once."
msgstr ""
"&appname; podpira sledenje izposoj vseh vnosov v zbirki. "
"<interface>Pogovorno okno za izposojo</interface> lahko odprete z uporabo "
"menijske postavke <guilabel>Odjava</guilabel> ali z desnim klikom na vnos. "
"Več vnosov je mogoče odjaviti hkrati."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The borrower's name may be directly entered, or pulled from the default "
"&kde; address book by clicking on the button next to the name entry. The "
"check-out date is assumed to be the current date, but may be changed. The "
"due date is optional, and other notes may be added about the loan."
msgstr ""
"Ime izposojevalca je mogoče neposredno vnesti ali povzeti iz privzetega "
"&kde; adresarja s klikom na gumb poleg vnosa imena. Predvideva se, da je "
"datum odjave trenutni datum, vendar se lahko spremeni. Datum zapadlosti ni "
"obvezen, o izposoji pa se lahko dodajo še druge opombe."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a due date is entered, and &appname; is compiled with libkcal support, a "
"loan reminder may be added to the default &kde; calendar as a To-Do item. "
"&korganizer; can be used to view those items."
msgstr ""
"Če je vnesen datum zapadlosti, in &appname; je preveden s podporo za "
"libkcal, lahko privzeti &kde; koledar kot opravilo. &korganizer; lahko "
"uporabite za ogled teh elementov."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an entry is checked-out, the <emphasis>Loaned</emphasis> field is set "
"to <emphasis>true</emphasis>. If no loaned field exists in the collection, "
"one is added. Do not modify that field directly! Entries on-loan may be "
"checked-in using the menu item, or right-clicking on an entry in the "
"<interface>Loan View</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vnos odjavljen, je polje <emphasis>Izposojeno</emphasis> nastavljeno "
"na <emphasis>true</emphasis>. Če v zbirki ni polja izposoje, se eno doda. Ne "
"spreminjajte tega polja neposredno! Izposojene vnose je mogoče prijaviti z "
"uporabo menijske postavke ali z desnim klikom na vnos v <interface>Pogled "
"izposoje</interface>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The &appname; <interface>Loan Dialog</interface></screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno za izposojo</interface></"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: fundamentals.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &appname; <interface>Loan Dialog</interface></phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&appname; <interface>Pogovorno okno za izposojo</interface></phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Tips"
msgstr "Splošni nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a book has more than one author, you should separate their names by a "
"semi-colon, so that Tellico will know to split them and use them separately. "
"Any other field which allows multiple values should be entered the same way. "
"with a semi-colon (;) separating each value."
msgstr ""
"Če ima knjiga več kot enega avtorja, morate njihova imena ločiti s "
"podpičjem, da jih bo Tellico znal razdeliti in uporabiti ločeno. Vsa druga "
"polja, ki dovoljujejo več vrednosti, je treba vnesti na enak način. s "
"podpičjem (;), ki ločuje vsako vrednost."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change which fields are shown in the list view by right-clicking on "
"the column header."
msgstr ""
"Polja, ki so prikazana v pogledu seznama, lahko spremenite tako, da z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknete glavo stolpca."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add, edit, or modify the fields in the collection using the "
"<interface>Collection Fields Dialog</interface>. The arrow buttons below the "
"field list can be used to change the position of the field in the list, "
"which affects the placement in the entry editor."
msgstr ""
"Polja v zbirki lahko dodajate, urejate ali spreminjate s pomočjo "
"<interface>Pogovorno okno Polja zbirke</interface>. S puščičnimi gumbi pod "
"seznamom polj lahko spremenite položaj polja na seznamu, kar vpliva na "
"postavitev v urejevalnik vnosov."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can edit more than one entry at a time, by holding down the &Shift; or "
"&Ctrl; key and selecting multiple entries."
msgstr ""
"Urejate lahko več kot en vnos hkrati, tako da držite &Shift; ali &Ctrl; "
"tipko in izbiro več vnosov."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can convert an existing book collection to a bibliography, which can "
"then be exported to bibtex or Bibtexml format."
msgstr ""
"Obstoječo knjižno zbirko lahko pretvorite v bibliografijo, ki jo lahko nato "
"izvozite v format bibtex ali Bibtexml."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If more than one field is formatted as a name, then an additional group "
"named \"People\" is added to the collection, allowing authors and editors to "
"be sorted or printed together, for example."
msgstr ""
"Če je kot ime oblikovano več kot eno polje, se zbirki doda dodatna skupina z "
"imenom »Ljudje«, ki omogoča na primer razvrščanje ali tiskanje avtorjev in "
"urednikov skupaj."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the appearance of the printed output by modifying the "
"<filename>tellico-printing.xsl</filename> file. The file generates &HTML;, "
"and the &CSS; within the stylesheet governs things like the font, the "
"margins, etc."
msgstr ""
"Videz natisnjenega izpisa lahko spremenite tako, da spremenite datoteko "
"<filename>tellico-printing.xsl</filename>. Datoteka ustvari &HTML; in &CSS; "
"v slogovni tabeli ureja stvari, kot so pisava, robovi itd."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-clicking an entry item opens the <interface>Entry Editor</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Dvoklik na postavko vnosa odpre <interface>Urejevalnik vnosov</interface>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add &HTML; tags to any <link linkend=\"para\"><emphasis>Paragraph</"
"emphasis></link> field for formatting, such as &lt;b&gt;<emphasis role=\"bold"
"\">bold</emphasis>&lt;/b&gt; or &lt;i&gt;<emphasis>italic</emphasis>&lt;/"
"i&gt;."
msgstr ""
"Dodate lahko &HTML; oznake za katero koli polje <link linkend=\"para"
"\"><emphasis>Odstavek</emphasis></link> za oblikovanje, kot je &lt;b&gt;"
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">krepko</emphasis>&lt;/b&gt; ali &lt;i&gt;"
"<emphasis>ležeče</emphasis>&lt;/i&gt;."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <interface>Column View</interface>, you can press a letter on the "
"keyboard to skip to the next entry that starts with that letter."
msgstr ""
"V <interface>Pogled stolpcev</interface> lahko pritisnete črko na "
"tipkovnici, da preskočite na naslednji vnos, ki se začne s to črko."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use derived values to combine values from multiple fields into a "
"single value. Just check the derived value box and use a value template "
"similar to \"<userinput>Value: %{fielda}%{fieldb}</userinput>\" where %{...} "
"gets replaced with the appropriate field value. This is useful to collect "
"multiple values in a single field, &eg; for better grouping, and to combine "
"fields of different types by respecting proper sorting at the same time. "
"Consider for example a number field followed by a text subfield with entries "
"3b, 14a."
msgstr ""
"Izpeljane vrednosti lahko uporabite za združevanje vrednosti iz več polj v "
"eno samo vrednost. Preprosto potrdite polje za izpeljano vrednost in "
"uporabite predlogo vrednosti, podobno »<userinput>Vrednost: "
"%{fielda}%{fieldb}</userinput>«, kjer se %{...} nadomesti z ustrezno "
"vrednostjo polja. To je uporabno za zbiranje več vrednosti v enem polju, "
"npr. za boljše združevanje in združevanje polj različnih tipov ob "
"upoštevanju pravilnega razvrščanja hkrati. Vzemimo na primer številsko "
"polje, ki mu sledi besedilno podpolje z vnosi 3b, 14a."
